cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.GR 

The paper deals with visual scene perception and clustering, which are core topics in computer vision (cs.CV) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI). The use of appearance statistics and distance metrics also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG) and neural networks (cs.NE). Finally, the use of graph theory and connectivity suggests a possible connection to computer graphics (cs.GR).
